title: has pixel phone support for OMACP?
content:
My Mobile operator is trying to configure the APN via OMACP, but it doesn't work.
Can anybody confirm if pixel has support for OMACP?

More info at:
OMA Client Provisioning (CP) https://www.openmobilealliance.org/wp/
https://www.openmobilealliance.org/release/ClientProv/

If not, it's possible to configure the apn downloading a file via wifi ?
